Name: UCSB

Name: Glass Beach
Description: A place in my hometown to look at the Napa River. The beach is full of pieces of glass washing up on the sand. The beach is extremely small, but it's a nice place to walk to and look out.

Description: A McDonald's connected to a gas station. It was a common place for me to go to get food and hang out with friends in a park nearby.
